    "It is observed that the AUC scores for Spider consistently surpass those for BIRD (and BIRD w/ EK).",
    "We hypothesize that this disparity is stemmed from the prevalence of ambiguous schemas in BIRD.",
    "Additionally, incorporating external knowledge enhances classification accuracy in BIRD, especially when the external knowledge directly highlights tables and columns relevant to the question.",
    "In supervised CodeS fine-tuning, we set 𝑡𝑜𝑝 𝑘1 and 𝑡𝑜𝑝 𝑘2 to 6 and 10.",
    "For few-shot incontext learning, to accommodate more demonstrations in the input prompt, these are adjusted to 5 and 6."
